text: Five Star Chicken is a Thai poultry fast food restuarant since 1985 in Ladpao 80 St. in Bangkok, Thailand. == History == In Ladpao 80 street in the capital of Thailand, Bangkok. The fast food restaurant has over 8,000 restaurants across 9 countries. == References == == Other websites == Category:1980s establishments in the Philippines Category:1985 establishments in Asia Category:Fast-food restaurants Category:Companies of Thailand
